            <p class="lead mb-4 opacity-90">Click below to start a WhatsApp conversation right now</p>
            <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
                <a href="https://wa.me/2348082232578?text=Hello%20Fodan%20Artistry%2C%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20your%20artwork%20collection." 
